Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:01:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna hurl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What brought this on, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:01:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have become hooked on Marimite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Marimite?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a kid!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start copying their costumes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that called cosplay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I already do plenty of that at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You work at one of those places...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Kona-chan was a high-class lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels so wrong that I can't even picture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Baseball games have been going over schedule too much recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do the people watching new anime get shafted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to watch anime that badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you could get cable or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't there specialized channels for that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,God knows I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But the cable guys were all, like, {Quotative like again.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"You can't get cable..." {Why is there an ellipse anyway?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You look kinda down. Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I went to have my cavity taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... You went to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are there so many follow-up trips after a visit to the dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it isn't just one or two trips!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.86,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to see you looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan's so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's talking the same way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't feel weird at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And she isn't even questioning the way Kona-chan's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen a person say "good day" in real life! {Should the first word in the qutoation marks be capitalised?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears to be a regularly used greeting... {Maybe is "common" instead of "regularly used" here?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the girls' school my friends go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A real school for rich girls is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How refined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroi told me to collect the summer homework for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent work, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Seba-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Butlers must be named Sebastian, do you not agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You do get that impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't happening! Tell us a funny story, Sebastian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacation just ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but you ain't got no time to be mooching around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Start thinking about your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...and put effort into studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By future, she means choosing a major.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess high school is only a temporary stopping point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you probably haven't done much thinking about the future, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You chose liberal arts to be in the same class with everyone else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsu-Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You blabbed! Ah, sorries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you told her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...o-of all people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have just been honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate being lonely, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For my summer homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I did as you told me and wrote down random stuff when I didn't know the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...and now I have to redo it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get help from me, you might have to redo it again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if you know what I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She got out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,An extension on homework without an extension on summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should borrow Kagami's notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of cicadas puts me to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The schedule's off because the baseball game went over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it can be useful sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My recorder's off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are your glasses, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They broke this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot that I left them on the chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...and accidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but may I borrow your notes for today later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You still got the clumsy thing going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your handwriting is a mystery to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing we have the same teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But please keep this a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wish to ruin their good intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for letting me use your notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to thank us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected Yuki-chan to borrow my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not happening again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In games, when a character who wears glasses up shows at school without them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they suddenly become popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess that doesn't happen in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It really doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't chocolate cornets kinda look like drills?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Drills...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Didn't we discuss which side of a chocolate cornet was the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how the thin end looked like the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the fat end looks more like the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one big bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And layers of stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When the lower half of your body gains weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...then it becomes difficult to buy skirts and the like. {Doesn't make sense. Replace the "the" with a "it"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use your waist measurements, you can't get it over your hips.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If it fits your hips perfectly, it's loose around your waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no choice but to buy one that's too big for your waist...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...and when you walk around in it, your skirt starts spinning, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A body with layers of stomach looks like a cornet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you turn it on the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you can play it like a cornet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you turn it again, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...put it on your head like a cornet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that supposed to be funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you dieting to make up for the added summer weight, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But my weight went down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...without my waist or hips changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the fruits of your diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's plain to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that when you diet, you lose weight in the places you don't want to first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay already! {Use "enough" here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When reading literature,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the trick is to keep the theme in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and understand what the author is trying to convey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.73,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that people with poor eyesight end up with nasty expressions that scare other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...it depends on the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When you said it depends on the person...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...you glanced over at me, didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that thinner eyes make you look prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes you look more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Way too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who's always complaining about night games lasting too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...shouldn't be so loose with time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All the games have been going over schedule lately, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it infected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it's contagious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you late?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Overslept?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give me an adult reason for why you were late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There was still plenty of time left when I finished getting ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So to kill time... {"In order..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...I started playing games and couldn't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worse than a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a bunch of cultural festivals and sporting events during the second semester, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have tests soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan is really athletic, so she can do well in sporting events.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like sporting events 'cause they make me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty rare to see such an athletic sit-inside-all-day type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what our class will do for the cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything I'd want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,These things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...can never be decided,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,unless someone wants to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person who brings up the idea usually gets put in charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so nobody's willing to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have to stay after school to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to watch evening anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn to cook dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have to stop by the store on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's favorite chicken curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in our family loves chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that letting curry sit overnight makes it taste better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It works well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll make some extra and bring it for lunch tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Since there'll be leftovers anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Hiiragi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you calling so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The curry I made yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I let it sit overnight and it's spoiled now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry usually doesn't go bad in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you put in anything weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...there was mold in it this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Another cornet today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They taste good, so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but the difference between when your lunches are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...made properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...or made frugally...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...is really obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa and I take turns in making lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good with housework...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It always ends up being simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry it's frugal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the type of person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...who can blow up pots when they cook!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody in the world can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan's lunch looks wonderful again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lunch is just leftovers from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner at Miyuki-san's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is really fancy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are just the leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's inside these fried eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We had some eel leftover last night, so I added it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't usually see leftovers for eel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that's ever left over at our house is moldy curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your house isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They bought me a cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I did well on my practical exams for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your number.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what my number was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata. Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I usually forget it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Dad's the only one who ever calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that defeat the purpose of having a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Keroro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They bought it for me with the cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a girl in our class who had a bunch of straps on her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They weighed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the straps alone were 800 grams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's heavy, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she took the straps off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...her stiff shoulders were cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like making a phone call would count as weight training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it exciting how you never know when you'll get a call on your cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope someone calls me soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to get so excited over a cell phone nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you find your number yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In England,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a large struggle between the House of Lancaster and the House of York.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The two houses fought wearing red and white roses respectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, this war was known as the War of Roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It lasted from 1455 to 1485.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mine!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody finally called me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick it up in the faculty office after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But junk mail already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Still at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking with Konata and Miyuki and lost track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little late and look what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with Kona-chan and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he'd get the idea after calling one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fathers are always worried about their daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We sure get a lot of junk mail these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to make your address hard to guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My e-mail address is in roman letters:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,iluvgirlswithglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go with maids or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But maids and shrine maidens are popular and easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We get it already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...so don't talk so loudly around the general public.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your conversation is a bigger problem than the junk mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My cell phone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She left it in her pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone to a better place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll buy me another one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenacious little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the e-mail last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that said Kagami wanted her notes back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last one you sent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:28.42,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You never respond immediately when you get an e-mail, do you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't reply to people I can talk to whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Reply to e-mails through e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We see each other every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to lose your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that big of a deal anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't decide that on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And she didn't return my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This manga I borrowed from Kona-chan moved me to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the manga, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it so stupid and hilarious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It moved me to tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to believe you're talking about the same manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cry, you're with Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you laugh, you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be classified with either of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanna see how Onee-chan reacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it wrong to want to know more about your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Attack No. 1 make you cry or laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry. Laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's your favorite manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sgt. Frog. Sgt. Frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell if these two are similar or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join a manga club, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you love manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd be willing to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'd be a good use of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw. Draw. Draw. Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you even try on this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, Konata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this a picture of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I could really stretch and say that you captured her spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can breathe fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It fits Kagami-san's image so perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What a frightening child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut that out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a new volume of FMP out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I guess there's a release date coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading to Gamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just stop by a local bookstore today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some other stuff to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to come with me as a sign of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are clingy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you shouldn't be using words like friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to give me your purchase points as a sign of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your idea of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.98,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You've waited so long for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she mad about how I mixed up the ribbons on my twintails with sunflowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It started already...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Before they change the channel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wanted to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, we're on another episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shiraishi Minoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama's in a bad mood, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You said your own name before the name Kogami Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not understand what natural order is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:21:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like those twintails of yours have been getting ridiculously popular in certain places.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I wouldn't call it popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be getting full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,People were expecting Project Fashionable Akira to show me in twintails, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with twin drills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Twin drills!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the Getter's speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No. 2, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The age of twintails is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The new thing is twin drills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what Konata said?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Drills are like a man's romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it now... {Timer's Note: Maybe this line can change to Romance, Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can catch the rest of this on the radio show and our home page!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look forward to next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,About those twintails...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the ones I had?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones in the real life picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You had sunflowers on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That looked awfully familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years ago was it? In one of my...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.55,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:21:58.75,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ew! Ew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was cute and wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it so nerve-wracking when you're singing your first song?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You wonder if your voice can be heard and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki's next, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing us something full of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have the mic?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm not used to this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me if it offends your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This ties in to the other Miyuki.
