Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:52.29,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,This is a new kind of moe. {"kind"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:54.65,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,You're so cool, Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I'm already out of time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.69,0:23:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't Need Me to Have a Blast."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to next time!
